      <title>斯洛伐克仍寻求在年底前与乌克兰达成天然气过境协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/slovakia-seeking-gas-deal-by-year-end-economy-minister-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯洛伐克副总理兼经济部长德尼莎·萨科娃表示，斯洛伐克计划在今年年底前达成协议，允许天然气继续从俄罗斯通过乌克兰输送。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/slovakia-seeking-gas-deal-by-year-end-economy-minister-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 16:11:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波罗的海国家将开始检查运输俄罗斯石油的油轮的保险状况</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/baltic-countries-to-start-checking-insurance-status-of-tankers-moving-russia-oil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[12 个欧洲国家将对在全球范围内运输数百万桶俄罗斯石油的油轮进行严厉打击，要求了解如何保护这些油轮免受石油泄漏和其他高昂索赔的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/baltic-countries-to-start-checking-insurance-status-of-tankers-moving-russia-oil</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 15:36:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴里克可能因与政府的争端而关闭马里矿场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/barrick-may-close-mali-gold-mine-over-dispute-with-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴里克黄金公司表示，马里军政府已经阻止了该国最大金矿的货运，如果货运继续暂停，该公司将需要停止该矿的作业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/barrick-may-close-mali-gold-mine-over-dispute-with-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 12:56:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
